title: The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-28-2013 THURS
description:
The Mike Rosen Radio Show NOV-28-2013 THURS


Thursday, November 28, 2013
  
THANKSGIVING 2013

 
 

 - 9AM hour

Guest host, Jon Caldara. 1.Jon critiques Denver Post editorial on Evie Hudak resignation. 

2. Should stores open on Thanksgiving?




 - 10AM hour

1. Is it worth it saving $500 on a TV if you have to wait in line for 72 hours? 

2. Jon relates John Stossel's account of the true story of the first Thanksgiving.

3. Presidential pardoning of the Thanksgiving turkey.




 - 11AM hour

1. Kid gets hit by meteorite. 

2. 200 year old cookie recipe must be changed because it contains trans fats which are outlawed.
